title:Baked Ziti
ingredients:1 package (16 oz.) Ziti, uncooked//
1 lb. ground beef//
1 onion, finely chopped//
2 cloves garlic, minced//
3 cups spaghetti sauce//
1/2 cup red wine (optional)//
1 teaspoon oregano leaves//
1 teaspoon dried basil, salt, and pepper//
2 cups shredded mozzarella cheese
instructions:Prepare pasta.//
Cook only 7 minutes and drain.//
Mix cooked beef, pasta, spaghetti sauce, wine and seasonings in large bowl.//
Pour into 13x9 inch baking dish.//
Sprinkle with cheese.//
Bake at 350F for 30 minutes.